Format: PNG (image/png)
Dimensions: 192x192 pixels
Color Profile: sRGB
Bit Depth: 32-bit (with alpha channel)
Maximum File Size: 32KB

Design Specifications:
1. Layout:
- Safe Zone: 77px centered square (40% of total dimensions)
- Internal Padding: 16px on all sides
- Background: #F5F5F5 (light gray)
- Primary Color: #1B4D89 (deep blue)

2. Design Elements:
- Primary Icon: Stylized map marker incorporating Pi symbol
- Egyptian Elements: Subtle hieroglyphic-inspired decorative elements
- Material Design: Flat design with subtle elevation shadows
- Maskable Support: All critical elements within safe zone

3. Technical Requirements:
- Transparent background for flexible platform display
- Anti-aliased edges for crisp rendering
- Optimized paths for pixel-perfect display
- High-DPI support for retina displays

4. Platform-Specific Considerations:
- Android: Maskable icon format support
- Chrome Web Store: Optimized for store listing
- Pi Browser: Enhanced visibility in platform context
- PWA: Standard compliant for home screen display

5. Optimization Guidelines:
- PNG compression: Optimized for size/quality balance
- Path optimization: Simplified vectors for clean scaling
- Color optimization: Limited palette for file size reduction
- Edge preservation: Maintain crispness after compression

Implementation Notes:
- Export with PNG-8 format where possible for size optimization
- Use indexed color palette to reduce file size
- Implement proper gamma correction for cross-platform display
- Include metadata for PWA manifest compatibility